PrecisAcceptance of an Instrument (CONDITIONAL ABSOLUTE SURRENDER) wherein the SHUSWAP BAND surrenders all its rights in any timber, sand, gravel, clay, wild grasses and non-metallic substances on some 198 hectares of land on SHUSWAP INDIAN RESERVE NO. 0 in British Columbia, which may be used, destroyed or removed pursuant to any lease of the lands.
